import { FormControl, VStack,FormLabel } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

const SignupPage = () => {
  return (
    <VStack spacing="5px">
        <FormControl>
            <FormLabel>Email</FormLabel>
            <Input 
            placeholder="Email" />

        </FormControl>

    </VStack>
  )
}

export default SignupPage
